data.description: Welcome to your dream home, a remarkable craftsman-styled masterpiece built in 2015. Nestled in a picturesque location, this property offers water views and the luxury of deeded beach access, allowing you to indulge in the coastal lifestyle.  As you step through the inviting front door, you'll immediately notice the exquisite craftsmanship and attention to detail. The interior is adorned with oil rubbed bronze doorknobs and plumbing fixtures, adding a touch of elegance and sophistication to every room.  The kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring pecan cabinets with oil rubbed bronze knobs, granite countertops, and a subway tiled backsplash. Prepare culinary delights while enjoying the panoramic water views and the natural light that fills the space.  Throughout the main living areas, you'll find hand scraped engineered hardwood floors that exude warmth and character. These floors create a seamless flow and enhance the charm of the craftsman style. The bathrooms are beautifully tiled, while the upstairs bedroom boasts plush carpeting and an en-suite with tasteful tile accents.  Storage is never an issue in this home, thanks to the walk-in attic storage, providing ample space for all your belongings. The home is also equipped with a Generac whole house generator. There is a 2 story garage that can fit you RV and all your outdoor gear  The outdoor oasis awaits you with a magnificent 13,950-gallon saltwater vinyl liner in-ground pool, complete with a Pentair cleaner, pump, filter, and salt chlorinator (6 years old).   The kitchen is equipped steel appliances, including a microwave drawer, perfect for culinary enthusiasts. The adjacent laundry room boasts a Kenmore Connect HE washer and dryer, offering efficiency and ease for your laundry needs.
